// BP_ShadowShard — Blueprint subclass of AShadowShardPuzzleActor
// Location: /Game/Game/Blueprints/Actors/BP_ShadowShard

/*
To create in UE5 Editor:
1. Create new Blueprint class extending AShadowShardPuzzleActor
2. Set default properties:
   - PuzzleName = "Shadow Shard Alpha"
   - RequiredArchetype = ShadowWalker
   - LightIntensity = 3000
   - LightRadius = 600
   - LightColor = FLinearColor(0.3, 0.1, 0.6) (violet)
   - ActiveMaterial = M_ShadowShard_Active (void violet glow)
   - InactiveMaterial = M_ShadowShard_Inactive (dim)
   - ActivationSound = S_ShadowShard_Activate_Cue
   - MeshComp → StaticMesh = SM_Shard_Crystal
3. Place 3x instances in PrototypeRoom at:
   - (400, 0, 100)
   - (200, -300, 100)
   - (0, -600, 100)
*/
